{"TopicId":191900,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Sun mod for better light/flares?","CreatedByName":"Jimbodiah","CreatedById":152759,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-24T15:42:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jimbodiah","CreatedById":152759,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-24T15:42:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlaying RSSVE/Scatterer and kind of disappointed by the sun, it\u0027s just a white dot in the sky and you wouldn\u0027t know it was the sun if it wasn\u0027t bigger than the other stars.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIs there any mod currently for 1.8.1 that adds better sun light and/or flares? I use to have some mods in the 1.3.1 days, but it seems there is not a lot around anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shadowmage","CreatedById":138730,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-24T20:57:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223746512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022191900\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221582558932\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152759\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jimbodiah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Jimbodiah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlaying RSSVE/Scatterer and kind of disappointed by the sun, it\u0027s just a white dot in the sky and you wouldn\u0027t know it was the sun if it wasn\u0027t bigger than the other stars.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIs there any mod currently for 1.8.1 that adds better sun light and/or flares? I use to have some mods in the 1.3.1 days, but it seems there is not a lot around anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI never got into it, but I\u0027m pretty sure that Scatterer will let you replace the sunflare entirely (with something custom?)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/LGhassen/Scatterer/tree/master/scatterer/Effects/SunFlare\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/LGhassen/Scatterer/tree/master/scatterer/Effects/SunFlare\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least that is what the source code makes me believe (though I haven\u0027t dug into it much)...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jimbodiah","CreatedById":152759,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-25T02:17:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that isn\u0027t working at the moment, at least I just get a white dot with no real lightsource using just Scatterer. Found the old Maar mod, but that only works 50% of the times I start KSP up.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Sun181.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002263.69\u0022 height=\u0022652\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022http://jimbodiah.com/ksp/Sun181.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-02-25T13:54:06Z\u0022 title=\u002202/25/2020 01:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 25, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Jimbodiah\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jimbodiah","CreatedById":152759,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-25T13:47:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMight be \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E/RSSVE getting in the way. In map view it seems to work more often than in regular view using Sunflares of Maar.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nLooks cool when is does work though.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Sun181_2.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002253.28\u0022 height=\u0022545\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022http://jimbodiah.com/ksp/Sun181_2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-02-25T14:22:32Z\u0022 title=\u002202/25/2020 02:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 25, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Jimbodiah\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-25T22:23:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to Add-On Discussions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jimbodiah","CreatedById":152759,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-26T19:47:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAH thanks!!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd the question is still relevant: Anyone know a mod that still works in 1.8.1 ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-26T20:23:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152759-jimbodiah/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022152759\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152759-jimbodiah/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Jimbodiah\u003C/a\u003E Speak of the devil. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E I\u0027m betting RSSVE has obsolete, broken sunflare configs. scatterer has had a few breaking updates recently, after all, one of which was the change of config syntax at about KSP 1.6.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-26T21:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m playing stock, no idea if this works with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E, but Scatterer together with good old GSF works perfectly for me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jimbodiah","CreatedById":152759,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-26T23:40:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGSF?\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167617-jadeofmaar/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167617\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167617-jadeofmaar/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@JadeOfMaar\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 \u00A0So it\u0027s related to these other mods? Maybe I can disable the sun flares in those to see if they are interfering.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-27T11:32:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223747897\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022191900\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221582760421\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152759\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jimbodiah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Jimbodiah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGSF?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022150430\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9605569943\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/138919-131-galileos-sun-flares-v183/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill works perfect with the latest Scatterer, you might want to check the screenshots in that thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hohmannson","CreatedById":202712,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-29T02:11:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022150430\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1363645730\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/171820-ksp-142-flare-replacer-v103-01-april-2018/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScatterer flares are a problem, something is causing them to vanish randomly. Seen that on multiple planet packs since\u00A0 KSP 1.7.3.\u00A0Try that thing, it can run alongside scatterer and the flare\u00A0will behave properly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223747058\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022191900\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221582638458\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152759\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jimbodiah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/25/2020 at 4:47 PM, Jimbodiah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMight be \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E/RSSVE getting in the way. In map view it seems to work more often than in regular view using Sunflares of Maar.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nLooks cool when is does work though.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://jimbodiah.com/ksp/Sun181_2.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Sun181_2.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002253.28\u0022 height=\u0022545\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022http://jimbodiah.com/ksp/Sun181_2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt. Hunt","CreatedById":97860,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-29T04:12:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI should point out that scatterer hasn\u0027t been updated for 1.9.x yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: I just noticed that the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E was asking specifically for 1.8.1, not 1.9.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-02-29T04:13:09Z\u0022 title=\u002202/29/2020 04:13  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 29, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Capt. Hunt\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}